<h4>Turbo Native Integration</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300/75">Configuration for Turbo Native mobile apps. See <%= link_to "Jumpstart Pro iOS", "https://jumpstartrails.com/ios", target: :_blank %> and <%= link_to "Jumpstart Pro Android", "https://jumpstartrails.com/android", target: :_blank %>.</p>

<h5 class="mt-8">Apple Push Notifications</h5>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300/75">To send native push notifications to iOS devices, you'll need to use the Apple Push Notification Service. Enabling this adds the Apnotic dependency for Noticed.</p>

<div class="my-2 custom-control custom-checkbox toggle">
  <%= f.check_box :apns, value: true, checked: Jumpstart.config.apns?, class: "form-checkbox" %>
  <%= f.label :apns, "Apple Notifications", class: "mb-0" %>
</div>
<p class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300/75">Don't forget to follow the <%= link_to "iOS documentation in Noticed", "https://github.com/excid3/noticed/blob/master/docs/delivery_methods/ios.md", target: :_blank %> to configure your credentials.</p>

<h5 class="mt-8">Android Notifications</h5>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300/75">To send native push notifications to Android devices, you'll need to use Firebase Cloud Messaging. Enabling this adds the GoogleAuth dependency for Noticed.</p>

<div class="my-2 custom-control custom-checkbox toggle">
  <%= f.check_box :fcm, value: true, checked: Jumpstart.config.fcm?, class: "form-checkbox" %>
  <%= f.label :fcm, "Android Notifications" %>
</div>
<p class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300/75">Don't forget to follow the <%= link_to "FCM documentation in Noticed", "https://github.com/excid3/noticed/blob/master/docs/delivery_methods/fcm.md", target: :_blank %> to configure your credentials.</p>
